title: Bangkok Voters at Polling Station in Thailand
description: Thai voters headed to the polls on Sunday in a three-cornered contest between the ruling Bhumjaithai Party, the progressive People’s Party and the populist Pheu Thai Party. (Source: Bloomberg)
